LAN Connectors
---------------

2 x **LAN (RJ45) connectors** provide Ethernet connectivity over standardized Ethernet cables. The integrated two-port Ethernet interface supports 10/100/1000BASE-T/TX specifications with automatic speed negotiation and Wake on LAN (WoL) functionality. Power over Ethernet (PoE) is not supported. 

.. rst-class:: text-center

   |lan_img|

   *2 x RJ45 GbE LAN Connectors*

.. note::
  
   Use CAT5 or better cables to achieve full data throughput over maximum distance defined by the 1000BASE-T standard (100m).
     
:pagebreak:`True`
